Description:
Stylish, Modern Family Living
Sale by Set Date 23/8/2011
A fantastic opportunity to secure a magnificent architectural designed home situated in a great sought after location. Within a short walking distance to all amenities including: recreational facilities, parklands, public transport, shops, local schools and much more. This beautifully proportioned home offers a stunning wide entrance and an abundance of features with lots of space for all the family to relax. Bedroom accommodation is generous with luxurious main en-suite with spa and double vanities, the other three bedrooms consisting of WIRs, also adding large family retreat area where you would enjoy the most beautiful view from balcony. Downstairs offering powder room with shower, large laundry and a huge study area. Spacious family living areas, open plan meals area adjoining spacious modern kitchen boasting stainless steel appliances and granite bench top, also a second fully equipped kitchen. The further massive entertainment room ideal to gather family or friends together on a special occasion .With other highlights including hydronic heating throughout, evaporative cooling, ducted vacuum, beautiful light fitting, alarm system, inter-com, granite stone in all bathrooms and much more Set on 1000 Sqm of land, this 64 square home also features a larger than usual double garage with rear roller door and internal access suitable for trailer or boat with extra parking up to 5 cars for visitors, with this there are two separate driveways and entry's to the garage. This is the best pocket of Derrimut surrounded with quality neighbours.
Nathan (Nghia) Chu : 0403 126 139

Description:
READY MADE INVESTMENT
In a quiet pocket of the popular neighbourhood is this 4 Bedroom home located on approximately 500m2 block of land. This stylish and well thought out floor plan has separate living at each ends of the home giving a formal area the front of the home and a spacious family area at the rear.
Features of the home include:
* 4 Bedrooms, 2 Bathrooms
* Master bedroom with Ensuite and Walk in Robe
* Separate living areas, formal and informal
* Modern Kitchen including gas cook top
* Ducted heating plus split system cooling
* Double garage with remote and rear access
Providing all the essential items of the modern home with extras such as rear access, this affordable home would suit any prospective tenant or owner occupier.
Further amenities accessible from this convenient location are the local primary school, parklands, shopping centre, and easy access to the western ring road with a direct route of 22km (approx) right to the heart of Melbourne's CBD.
Mel: 360 K2
First National Westwood (Sales)

Set in this quiet cul-de-sac, this beautiful residence delivers established gardens, privacy and an exceptional indoor/outdoor family environment. The layout incorporates multiple living zones including theatre room, family and dining room which progresses to a beautiful hostess kitchen boasting quality appliances. The undercover alfresco area features a lovely garden aspect. Generous bedrooms surround the children's retreat and sparkling central bathroom. Conveniently close to a selection of school, shops, public transport, parks and walking trails.

Description:
Motivated Vendor
What an opportunity, this is a great family home or investment, situated close to a large reserve within this sought after estate in Derrimut.
Close to Western Ring Road, Sunshine golf club, schools and local shops, Deer Park is just a stone's throw away.
In brief this neatly presented home offers 3 bedrooms all with BIR a generous two way bathroom, open and modern kitchen with dishwasher, 2 separate living areas, double garage with internal access for convenience.
Inspection is essential to appreciate what is on offer and the location. Auction takes place on Sat 5th March 1pm start with open for inspections on Saturdays between 12.30pm - 1pm.
To register your interest please contact Jay Radbourne 0422 280 465.

Description:
Family Home In A New Estate
Set in the new Brimbank Estate is this good size family home. A great investment opportunity with solid future growth. This property has great access to Ballarat Road, Western Ring Road, shops, schools & is close to the parks and the newly developed golf course.
Comprising: 4 bedrooms, master with en-suite and walk in robe, open living with contemporary
kitchen, meals and family areas, modern bathroom and double remote garage all on approx. 448 sqms of land.
Features: Stainless steel appliances, dishwasher, alarm, ducted heating and split system cooling.
